    venue: "Energies",
    year: 2021,
    type: "Journal",
    domains: ["energy"],
    link: "https://www.mdpi.com/1996-1073/14/23/8142",
    abstract:
      "A review of the development, policy, and socioeconomic context of solar power in the United States, including a novel five-tier categorization of US states by solar prospects, alongside prevalent technologies and applications.",
  },
  {
    title:
      "CVR-Net: A deep convolutional neural network for coronavirus recognition from chest radiography images",
    authors: "M. K. Hasan, M. A. Alam, M. T. E. Elahi, S. Roy, S. R. Wahid",
    venue: "arXiv preprint",
    year: 2020,
    type: "Preprint",
    domains: ["ml"],
    link: "https://arxiv.org/abs/2007.11993",
    abstract:
      "CVR-Net is a multi-scale, multi-encoder ensemble CNN that aggregates outputs from two encoders across scales to recognize COVID-19 from chest radiography images, evaluated across 2-, 3-, and 4-class tasks.",
  },
  {
    title:
      "Efficient Approach to Detect Epileptic Seizure using Machine Learning Models for Modern Healthcare System",
